Quickstrike stopped in his tracks when Black Arachnia passed by him. 
He watched as she went to Dark Mouse's quarters. He followed and 
waited by the frame of the door. He glared at her curiously. He would 
wait until she was finished with Dark Mouse or unilt she left the 
room.
